fields.name: Mini Digital Thermometer Hygrometer with Fahrenheit (℉) for Humidors, Greenhouse, Garden, Cellar
fields.description:
About this item
TWO IN ONE: The mini digital hygrometer thermometer with built-in probe, electronic thermometer and hygrometer for measuring temperature and humidity for indoor use.
WIDE TESTING RANGE: Humidity meters measuring range: -58℉-158℉ , humidity measuring range: 10%-99%RH.
HIGH PRECISION DISPLAY: Humidity Meter measurement accuracy: ±2℉, humidity measurement accuracy: ±5%RH.
EASY TO INSTALL: Our humidity meters gauge can help you to konw the current temperature and humidity, embedded opening size (1.81*1.06 inch) . If the size is not suitable, it can be fixed with double-sided tape.
WIDELY USED: The indoor thermometer hygrometer widely use in greenhouse, garden, guitar case, incubators, brooders, office, cellar, fridge, closet any other place that requires monitoring of temperature and humidity levels.

fields.name: Michu Cat Grass Seed Replacement Pack
fields.description:
Boost Your Cat's Health with Michu Cat Grass Seed Mulch Pack

Looking for a natural, effective snack for your furry friend? The Michu Cat Grass Seed Mulch Replacement Pack is the perfect solution! This product promotes healthy digestion and reduces hairball buildup, making it a must-have for any cat owner.

Crafted from premium seeds and mulch, this Cat Grass Grow Kit is easy to use. Just sprinkle the seeds on your cat's existing soil, water regularly, and watch your cat enjoy a nutritious snack. Get the Michu Cat Grass Seed Mulch Pack today for a happy, healthy cat!

fields.name: Kazoo Ripple Fish Wand Cat Toy
fields.description: This delightful fish-themed Play Wand is just the ticket for whiskered anglers who love a good play session. Its interactive nature and the enticing feathery fish design are perfect for staving off ennui, sparking an innate desire in cats to chase, stalk, and pounce. Plus, it's an ideal lure for enticing humans into engaging, bond-strengthening play. With an elastic rope adding dynamic movement, this toy is sure to keep your feline friend nimble and entertained. Infused with catnip, known for sending cats into a state of euphoria, and featuring a variety of textures, it's designed to appeal to a cat's primal hunting instincts.
